de.susebox.jtopas.impl
Class SequenceStore

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--de.susebox.jtopas.impl.SequenceStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
SequenceHandler
public class SequenceStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements SequenceHandler

This class is used by StandardTokenizerProperties to store and search special sequences, comments and strings. The class is not suitable for standalone use since it does not check parameters for null values etc. It assumes that these checks have been done in the calling module.

Author:
Heiko Blau
See Also:
StandardTokenizerProperties, SequenceHandler
